data.description: Welcome to your enchanting oasis in the heart of the city! This delightful Mid-Century Tudor Cottage Style Home offers a perfect blend of vintage charm and modern convenience. The painted stucco faade exudes curb appeal. Step inside to discover a maintained interior featuring paint throughout, highlighting the home's original character. The updated kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting contemporary amenities while preserving the home's timeless allure. This home boasts generously sized bedrooms, where some original fixtures add a touch of historic charm. Discover unique features like a root cellar/storage space, perfect for preserving your harvests or doubling as a workshop for your creative pursuits. Recent upgrades include a newer roof, water heater, and range oven, ensuring worry-free living for years to come. The property's large lot has been thoughtfully sectioned off for different uses, enhancing functionality and versatility. RV enthusiasts will appreciate the convenient alley access and RV parking. Located in a highly desirable neighborhood, this residence is just a stone's throw away from Parkview Hospital, Mineral Palace Park & I-25.
